  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nAdd a system for tracking storage writes to `txlog`, including a corresponding action type.  The action should include decoded information about what was written to and what was written to it.  Note that a single action should not correspond to a single `SSTORE`, but to a larger conceptual \"write\" -- e.g., if a string is written to, this should be a single action.  (Having array pushes/pops being two actions might be OK; this will need to be figured out.)",
